column3: 1.What is your ranking of the best sandwiches (i.e., your Personal Aggregate Ranking)?
column13: 2.What is your deliciousness score for each of the following sandwiches? Answers should be between 0 (not delicious) and 100 (Mike's cookies).
column23: 3.What is your heaviness score for each of the following sandwiches? Answers should be between 0 (Prick Stick) and 100 (depleted uranium).
column33: 4.What is your reliability score for each of the following sandwiches? Answers should be between 0 (student center Subway) and 100 (Om).
column43: 5.How many days per week would you be willing to eat each of the following sandwiches? Answers should be between 0 (student center Subway) and 7 (Mike's cookies).
column53: 6.How many days of recharge are required between consumption of each of the following sandwiches? Answers should be between 0 (Mike's cookies) and 1000 (student center Subway).
column63: 7.Which of the following sandwiches are the 3 most overrated? The sandwich for which you respond 1 is the most overrated (Lonzo).
column73: 8.Which of the following sandwiches are the 3 most underrated? The sandwich for which you respond 1 is the most underrated (Matt Prater).
